A stunning PVC over-bust, perfect for an hourglass figure. As this garment is moderate in length we have most success with ladies that are 5ft 8" & under. Best quality materials. The corset is manufactured to the highest standards & boasts the following features:

•1/2" Steel bones throughout
•Finished in highest quality PVC
•Full steel busk
•100% Cotton lining
•Modesty panel
•Heavy lacing to the back
•Modest straight line cut
•15" corset front & back
•Improve posture
•6 suspender loops (suspender clips sold separately)
•Zip front fastening

The cut of this corset makes it ideal for completely covering up, the garment will take 4" off your waistline if desired.

description:
A stunning PVC under-bust, perfect for creating an hourglass figure. As this garment is moderate in length we have most success with ladies that are 5ft 8" & under. Best quality materials. The corset is manufactured to the highest standards & boasts the following features:

Fashion corsets are perfect for lingerie and for dressing up on a Saturday night. Fashion corsets are less restrictive than steel boned corsets and a lot less hot and heavy. Corsets in this range are more for aesthetics will not pull your waist in. Plus size ladies or ladies with DD cup or over may feel more confident in a steel boned corset, Steel boned corsets offer more support and control.

•1/2" Steel bones throughout
•Finished in highest quality PVC
•Full steel busk
•Stylish new zip design
•Modesty panel
•Heavy lacing to the back
•13" corset front & back
•Improve posture
•6 suspender loops (suspender clips sold separately)
•Zip front fastening

The cut of this corset makes it ideal for completely covering up, the garment will take 4" off your waistline if desired.
